{"tid":738194,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"熱血膠band搵熱血結他手","createTime":"2018-07-11T10:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T11:03:25.000Z","uid":45583,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"60c3c765a93efd7c9887566d661c0bf027dd3848","tid":738194,"uid":45583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T10:39:48.000Z","msg":"介紹下成員，而家有四個人：<br />\n<br />\n結他手喺美國讀blues結他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最鍾意B.B. King。但歌路好闊，即jam嘅solo勁好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBass手基本功、音樂感良好。鍾意my chemical romance、the pretty reckless一類有少少dark嘅band。可以唱女backing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鼓手以前有打開酒吧show，任何歌都可以即jam。鍾意killersoap、k-on<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同日系動漫歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後vocal係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 寫詞寫曲主力，間中可以分身彈下琴同結他。鍾意Ellegarden、Pay money to my Pain，日本punk/emo嘢，中港台indie，歐美大路band都聽幾雜食。<br />\n<br />\n之前出過兩場細show，全部玩自己歌，歌路punk/pop/emo為主。成員廿歲頭，一星期夾一次。想搵鍾意punk，對編曲有火有諗法嘅結他手。有興趣tg：winterjai <br />\n<br />\n有demo"},{"pid":"24a376685f4afca0398a59d6930030530f1f20d0","tid":738194,"uid":45583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T11:09:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b9f3b547c9ae7fa269bc900ea533a10676e083","tid":738194,"uid":45583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T11:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca1bf0b8545abcd6d796bf07570bd06b675fed9","tid":738194,"uid":126133,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T11:40:33.000Z","msg":"仲以為熱狗添"},{"pid":"0a47fffcc277117ab0480d49fec78657cd14a548","tid":738194,"uid":28181,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2